properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 11 at 1:13PM EST until January 12 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Pittsburgh PA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 55 mph
expected.

* WHERE...In Pennsylvania, Westmoreland Ridges and Fayette
Ridges Counties. In Maryland, Garrett County. In West
Virginia, Ridges of Eastern Monongalia and Northwestern
Preston, Preston, Eastern Preston, Western Tucker and Eastern
Tucker Counties.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 1 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 1 PM EST SUNDAY
